name: Ohana
description: RECENTLY invested & incubated @Muru-D, a TELSTRA backed accelerator program in SGP, Ohana is a marketplace that helps you find your next home in the city. We hook you up with the right roommate vetted for you by an algorithm, in less than 6 minutes and lets you reserve an available spot in their place - be it in a co-living house or an occupied room for 3 months at a time.
